@startuml 04-transfer
title Sơ đồ tuần tự - Chuyển tiền P2P (Transfer)

show footbox

skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 1.2
skinparam roundCorner 8
skinparam noteBackgroundColor #FFF8DC
skinparam noteBorderColor #C0A030

actor "Người dùng" as User
participant "Front-end" as FE
participant "API Gateway" as GW
participant "Transaction\nService" as TS
participant "User Service" as US
participant "Wallet Service" as WS
database "transaction_db" as TDB
database "user_db" as UDB
database "wallet_db" as WDB
queue "ActiveMQ\n(transaction-notification)" as MQ
participant "Notification\nService" as NS

== 1. Nhập thông tin & xác nhận PIN ==
User -> FE : Nhập SĐT người nhận
FE -> GW : GET /api/v1/users/by-phone/{phone}
GW -> US : GET /api/users/by-phone/{phone}
US -> UDB : SELECT user BY phone
UDB --> US : recipient
US --> FE : { fullName, phone }
FE --> User : Hiện thông tin người nhận

User -> FE : Nhập số tiền, mô tả, PIN

note right of FE #E8F5E9
  **FE validate:** amount ≥ 1.000đ, PIN 6 số,
  balance (cached) đủ, sinh requestId = UUID v4.
end note

== 2. Gateway xác thực JWT ==
FE -> GW : POST /api/v1/transactions/transfer\nAuthorization: Bearer <JWT>\n{ requestId, toPhone, amount, pin, description }

note right of GW #E3F2FD
  **AuthGlobalFilter:** decode JWT (jti, userId, role, phone),
  check blacklist jti, inject X-User-Id/Role/Phone + X-Internal-Secret.
end note

GW -> US : GET /internal/users/validate?jti=...\nX-Internal-Secret: ***
US -> UDB : SELECT FROM invalidated_tokens WHERE jti = ?
UDB --> US : (rỗng → token còn hiệu lực)
US --> GW : 200 OK

== 3. Transaction Service xử lý ==
GW -> TS : POST /api/transactions/transfer\n+ header nội bộ

alt fromPhone == toPhone (tự chuyển)
    TS --> FE : 400 SELF_TRANSFER
    FE --> User : "Không thể tự chuyển cho mình"
end

== 3.1 Idempotency check ==
TS -> TDB : SELECT FROM transactions WHERE request_id = ?
TDB --> TS : existingTx (hoặc null)

note right of TS #FFEBEE
  **Idempotency:** SUCCESS/FAILED → trả kết quả cũ;
  PENDING → 400 DUPLICATE_TRANSACTION (chống double-submit).
end note

alt existingTx có SUCCESS/FAILED
    TS --> FE : Trả response của tx cũ
else existingTx có PENDING
    TS --> FE : 400 DUPLICATE_TRANSACTION
end

== 3.2 Xác thực PIN ==
TS -> US : POST /internal/users/verify-pin\n{ phone, pin }

note right of US #FFEBEE
  **PIN check + chống brute-force:** BCrypt match;
  sai 5 lần → khoá PIN 15 phút; đúng → reset attempts.
end note

US -> UDB : check + update pin_failed_attempts, pin_locked_until
UDB --> US : ok
alt PIN sai hoặc bị khoá
    US --> TS : 400 INVALID_PIN / PIN_LOCKED
    TS --> FE : 400 PIN_VERIFICATION_FAILED
    FE --> User : Hiển thị lỗi PIN
end
US --> TS : 200 OK

== 3.3 Lấy thông tin & kiểm tra trạng thái ==
TS -> US : POST /internal/users/batch\n{ phones: [fromPhone, toPhone] }
US -> UDB : SELECT users WHERE phone IN (...)
UDB --> US : 2 users
US --> TS : [fromUser, toUser]

note right of TS #FFF3E0
  **Kiểm tra:** sender/recipient không LOCKED,
  sender.kycStatus == VERIFIED.
end note

alt Một trong hai LOCKED / sender chưa KYC
    TS --> FE : 400 SENDER_LOCKED / RECIPIENT_LOCKED / KYC_NOT_VERIFIED
    FE --> User : Hiển thị lỗi
end

== 3.4 Tạo transaction PENDING ==
note right of TS #FFEBEE
  saveAndFlush để bắt race condition khi 2 request
  cùng requestId song song (UNIQUE constraint).
end note

alt INSERT thành công
    TS -> TDB : INSERT transactions\n(status = PENDING, type = TRANSFER,\n amount, fee = 0)
    TDB --> TS : transactionId
else DataIntegrityViolation (race condition)
    TS -> TDB : SELECT tx WHERE request_id = ?
    TDB --> TS : tx (đã thắng race)
    TS --> FE : Trả kết quả cũ (nếu đã final)\nhoặc 400 DUPLICATE_TRANSACTION
end

== 3.5 Gọi wallet-service trừ/cộng tiền ==
TS -> WS : POST /internal/wallets/transfer\n{ fromUserId, toUserId, amount,\n  transactionId, reason = "TRANSFER_OUT", note }

note right of WS #FFEBEE
  **WalletService.transfer:** idempotency by transactionId;
  lock 2 ví theo UUID order ascending (tránh deadlock);
  reset daily/monthly limit; check daily/monthly limit + balance.
end note

WS -> WDB : SELECT ... FOR UPDATE 2 wallets (theo UUID order)
WDB --> WS : fromWallet, toWallet

alt Wallet thành công
    WS -> WDB : UPDATE fromWallet.balance −= amount\nUPDATE toWallet.balance += amount\nINSERT 2 ledger entries\n(DEBIT TRANSFER_OUT, CREDIT TRANSFER_IN)
    WDB --> WS : ok
    WS --> TS : 200 "Chuyển tiền thành công"
else Wallet fail (số dư/hạn mức/ví khoá)
    WS --> TS : 400 INSUFFICIENT_BALANCE / LIMIT_EXCEEDED / WALLET_LOCKED
end

== 3.6 Finalize transaction ==
alt Wallet trả về SUCCESS
    TS -> TDB : UPDATE status = SUCCESS + status_history

    note right of TS #E8F5E9
      **Đảm bảo nhất quán:** publish JMS **sau khi**
      DB commit (afterCommit) — tránh notification "ma".
    end note

    TS -> MQ : JmsTemplate.convertAndSend(\n"transaction-notification",\nTransactionNotificationEvent)
    TS --> FE : 200 { transactionId, status }
    FE --> User : "Chuyển tiền thành công"
else Wallet trả về error
    TS -> TDB : UPDATE status = FAILED + status_history (lý do)
    TS --> FE : 400 TRANSFER_FAILED + message
    FE --> User : Hiển thị lỗi
end

== 4. Thông báo bất đồng bộ (qua ActiveMQ) ==
MQ -> NS : @JmsListener nhận event

note right of NS #FFF3E0
  Lưu 2 notification (sender DEBIT + receiver CREDIT),
  push WebSocket, gửi SMS (SpeedSMS) + Email (SendGrid).
end note

NS -> NS : Xử lý event

@enduml
